{"tid":1440583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"個市差我地就食粥水, 其實市好我地未又係食粥水","createTime":"2019-08-10T13:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T03:14:11.000Z","uid":155883,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3e6ef69e453ee5fd137f818e0649b260d188740f","tid":1440583,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"成日話經濟差會冇飯開, 講真經濟好我地未又係差唔多, <br />\n如果係咁既話, 點解我唔拉埋你班中產落水?"},{"pid":"c436cb76290a7ddba83a1f1dcfd0c28f40fb83f8","tid":1440583,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"要拉埋班有錢佬落水先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4abba9a6954d6faceea3f4b78f2973cf1041ee7a","tid":1440583,"uid":279938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"個市好又冇服務又貼錢買難受，個市唔好先剛剛好。"},{"pid":"201faa68dd0e8eb113cce2480fd094807618a93f","tid":1440583,"uid":290726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"五大訴求,缺一不可 <br />\n不分化，包括中產"},{"pid":"a18f5eb673ddb626a941bf39fcebddeefcab7612","tid":1440583,"uid":155883,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c436cb76290a7ddba83a1f1dcfd0c28f40fb83f8","tid":1440583,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"要拉埋班有錢佬落水先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:06:22.000Z","msg":"大家唔好以為市差就只有基層受害<br />\n老實講中產, 同班商家佬都差唔多<br />\n你搵得萬零銀, 好景就加你幾舊, 但班商家呢? 佢地有冇同你分享經濟成果<br />\n唔好景就炒鳩你 (但事實係要炒都炒班中層先啦, 你萬零銀佢慳得幾多?) <br />\n市道唔好, 佢地啲租金一樣冇得減, 冇生意照出糧, 啲貨賣唔出又擇死哂<br />\n<br />\n過去十年, 零售食住自由行條水搵好多, 但受惠既全部都係商人, 市民未一樣食粥水, 大陸人最好唔敢落黎, 好想見到波鞋街允記老闆CUT COST<br />\n<br />\n如果經濟好我冇得受惠, 點解我要驚經濟差?"},{"pid":"0030aaed87687e9a447fb1d2517230d94d3a11b5","tid":1440583,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201faa68dd0e8eb113cce2480fd094807618a93f","tid":1440583,"uid":290726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"五大訴求,缺一不可 <br />\n不分化，包括中產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:07:43.000Z","msg":"唔分化中產, 佢地都係打工仔, 大家都受害<br />\n我只係要拉埋班奶共又孤寒既商家佬落水"},{"pid":"219cf95aada71eb4c69b3d0bbb43f0717b61abd4","tid":1440583,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"我明白好多基層市民要養家唔敢罷工 或者上街食彈<br />\n我明白, <br />\n但唔該香港都係你屋企, 盡可能都幫少少<br />\n罷買係最低成本又好有效既抗爭方法<br />\n真係幫幫手<br />\n你落街經過都可能比黑警拉, 告你暴動<br />\n告唔入都48H<br />\n<br />\n但你唔買野, 冇人吹得你漲<br />\n幫幫手叫身邊所有人都唔好再消費<br />\n佢地比唔起租自然會反政府<br />\n<br />\n唔好為佢地(商家/ 管理層)著想, 市好佢地出緊一年花紅有冇分啲比你?<br />\n你都係出緊1個月花紅架咋<br />\n佢地都賺夠啦, 係時候要嘔返出黎"},{"pid":"9de0d7f637b0ddbdd7f038bc4c27d87ccdcec358","tid":1440583,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1806d786583936bcfdecb083a8f678a3a97fcbc9","tid":1440583,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=24OJX9A3136FiTY87siEPMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=dcc8c54e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1LFMotPfcLCi5MXxioVQX2E32ovPvizhH?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n[文宣］黑白大字報 政權罪行 遍地開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360258</a><br />\n<br />\n文宣就係做比藍絲、港豬<br />\n做比自己人睇有撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f01b8718ca10a223ed7c4bcd0d218e6a86bdae1e","tid":1440583,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"呃藍屍用"},{"pid":"8ca529c1d655a587be395329a01331187a059c45","tid":1440583,"uid":209547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:14:11.000Z","msg":"咁係你冇諗過市差可以有咩後果<br />\n正如修例通過你咪又係食竹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}